text: Mi tenniv i win I$at Oebbi, u t$atev: "jmaa $uoek, tameiiut ik, eezzeb i Oebbi"; teffrev deg iman ik, ayen ara d Isban Oebbi. Tugadev medden. D Oebbi, i iwatan a T tagwadev. Mi s ibra Zayed, Njewo ik yides, iwakken ur teppili lhejna i lmumnin, ma u$en tilawin n wid id ssekren, mara ad sent brun. Ad iuao lameo n Oebbi
